## Position
I am the head developer for [Galore Gaming](http://galoregaming.com) specializing in Bungee and Spigot plugins. Future projects will include other games such as CSGO and Chivalry.

## Development Team
Hire the Galore development team to work on your projects at [GaloreDevelopment](http://www.mc-market.org/threads/76680/#post-940959).
Fast, reliable plugin work with a lifetime guarantee on quality.
